            "heading": "How to Use",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/BT.Breakis1.jpg",
            "tab_image_width": 1000,
            "hide_image": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Every product page includes specific usage instructions, but here are a few general tips:</p><ul><li><strong>Powders &amp; Superfoods</strong> — Start with ½ to 1 tsp. Mix into smoothies, lattes, oatmeal, or baked goods.</li><li><strong>Loose Leaf Teas</strong> — Use 1–2 tsp per 8 oz of water. Steep at the recommended temperature for the best flavor.</li><li><strong>Spices &amp; Seasonings</strong> — Add to taste during cooking or as a finishing touch. A little goes a long way with high-quality ingredients.</li></ul><p>Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight to preserve freshness and potency.</p>",
