            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        },
        "tab_2": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients & Sourcing",
            "tab_image_width": 1000,
            "hide_image": false,
            "row_content": "<p>We source every ingredient directly from certified organic farms we know and trust — no middlemen, no compromises.</p><ul><li><strong>Certifications</strong> — USDA Organic, CCOF Certified</li><li><strong>Testing</strong> — Every batch independently lab-verified for purity, potency, heavy metals, and allergen safety</li><li><strong>Traceability</strong> — Full farm-to-shelf transparency on every product</li><li><strong>Free from</strong> — Synthetic additives, artificial colors, preservatives, fillers, and GMOs</li></ul><p>Check individual product listings for origin country, farm details, and batch-specific certifications.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "open_new_tab_1": false,
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        },
        "tab_3": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "tab_image_width": 1000,
            "hide_image": false,
            "row_content": "<h2>Returns policy</h2><ul><li>Dispatch: Within 24 Hours</li><li>Free shipping across all products on a minimum purchase of $50.</li><li>International delivery time - 7-10 business days</li><li>Cash on delivery might be available</li><li>Easy 30 days returns and exchanges</li></ul><h2>Shipping policy</h2><p>We offer standard and expedited shipping options at checkout. Standard shipping typically takes 3-7 business days, while expedited shipping arrives in 2-3 business days. Shipping costs are calculated based on the weight of the order and the selected shipping method. Free standard shipping is available on orders over $50.</p>",
